Description.value:
This is a template for scenario-specific synchronous outbound processing flows that you can copy and adapt to your needs:
- Configure the ProcessDirect sender adapter.
- In the "Set SAP headers" content modifier, maintain header SAP_MessageType of the receiver interface.
- Maintain mapping sequence and conversion routines of the request message if needed.
- Maintain mapping sequence and conversion routines of the response message if needed.
- Maintain exception handling to your needs.
- Add and maintain receiver adapter for the Request Reply flow step to connect to the receiving system
- Delete flow steps that you do not need.
For more details, please refer to the documentation (see link in Documents section of the package).
